name: Margie Huges
description: I am a sincere and open-minded lady, who loves to bring smiles to those who who surround me. I am not looking for a perfect man, I just dream to meet a real man who is mature enough to understand me and my thoughts, who is passionate about life, who knows, how to make his woman happy! I’m responsible and serious in my attitude towards life but yet romantic, and very sensual. I am an understanding, sincere and family-oriented woman. I know, how to make a comfort around my man, and I am not selfish in my relationships, because I value true feelings.
